events.text: The Thunder traded Jerami Grant to the Nuggets for a 2020 1st round pick (DEN).
The Hawks traded Omari Spellman to the Warriors for Damian Jones.
The Grizzlies traded Delon Wright to the Mavericks for a 2021 2nd round pick (DAL) and a 2022 2nd round pick (DAL).
The Pelicans traded Kenrich Williams, a 2020 2nd round pick (MIL), and a 2020 2nd round pick (NOP) to the Hornets for Willy Hernangomez.

born.loc: Tuzla, Republic of Bosnia and Herzegovina
